content: The President will be in town... like him, or not (this is not a political post, it's an informational post)  This is a Mass Transit kind of day New Yorkers!  FDR will be shut for a while as they motorcade the President up the East side to midtown.  Avoid the 50's between 5th and 6th Avenues, then they'll motorcade over to the Intrepid for a dinner that starts around 7pm.  He'll leave NYC at around 9ish and fly to New Jersey where he'll be for the rest of the weekend.  Plan accordingly and use Mass Transit.  Please share this post for all of your friends to see. #abc7NY  Lori Stokes Ken Rosato Bill Evans Meteorologist
